{"tid":878483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇廣州地鐵站人臉辨識安檢","createTime":"2018-10-27T07:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T14:32:35.000Z","uid":82228,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a024e91c72e2c38de933f1d1084fd66bfa27a323","tid":878483,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"據中共官媒報導，10月26日開始，廣州萬勝圍站A口、珠江新城站B1口、嘉禾望崗站B口及體育西路站E口等四個地鐵站點，開始試點，通過人臉識別功能實現乘客通行實名認證。<br />\n<br />\n實名認證通道安檢門前的立柱上裝有攝像頭和二維碼掃碼區。乘客需提前下載廣州地鐵官方APP，開通「智慧安檢」功能，「刷臉」後方可實名認證通過安檢通道。<br />\n<br />\n好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港豬繼續坐港鐵返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dc16811e1e37b6ae23c93a47409fbadf5444ce","tid":878483,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:22:42.000Z","msg":"唔裝個app係咪以後唔搭得地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0796a9a8b5ef6091db0880f831dbe6e4b4907ced","tid":878483,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e711901627405c1cbb17069fc3570ff8d30e2a9","tid":878483,"uid":149494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0796a9a8b5ef6091db0880f831dbe6e4b4907ced","tid":878483,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"即刻拉你出去除哂佢"},{"pid":"b9c58cfde81a933662bae0074143377cbc7dc8f5","tid":878483,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間要幾耐先可以落到月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb249e5d22d78fa4026470349f352ba7ed65256","tid":878483,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"難道中國人不需要管嗎？"},{"pid":"88b9b95495ebdf69a